&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are looking for a Senior Software Engineer who is excited to bring Pulumi’s cloud programming model to the world. You will be part of realizing a vision where every developer can harness the power of the cloud.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
