&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pulumi.com/docs/pulumi-cloud/esc/&quot;&gt;Pulumi ESC&lt;/a&gt; to tackle configuration complexity and secrets sprawl.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pulumi.com/product/internal-developer-platforms/&quot;&gt;Pulumi IDP&lt;/a&gt; to support teams to create golden paths with reusable components and templates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
